# Project-specific

## Stack

- Project: `SCOR Rotator`
- Language: `TypeScript`
- Framework: `Electron + Vite + React`

## Paths

- Source: `src/` (renderer), `electron/` (main/preload)
- Tests: co-located `*.test.ts` (Vitest)

## Conventions

- Airtable access only via Electron main IPC (`window.airtable`)
- Playback window via `window.playback` in Electron; browser popup fallback in Vite-only mode
- Secrets: `AIRTABLE_TOKEN` from 1Password-mounted `.env` — never commit real tokens
- Brand: import logos from `brand/logos/`; CSS vars from `src/styles/brand.css`
- Ignore Vite watch on `**/.env` (1Password mount)
